1. SEC and Ripple reached a preliminary settlement agreement, and both parties applied to suspend the appeal process;
2. Spot gold rose to $3217.97/ounce, setting a new record high;
3. A whale will unstake more than 140,000 SOL and transfer them to Kraken;
4. The founder of Silk Road will make his first public appearance at the Las Vegas Bitcoin Conference;
5. Arizona passed the Bitcoin Mining Rights Act;
6. Fed Goolsby: Now is the time for the Fed to suspend interest rate adjustments and wait and see;
7. The New Hampshire House of Representatives passed the Bitcoin Reserve Act;
8. Fed Governor Bowman hopes to conduct an independent review of the bank collapse in March 2023, which may involve SVB, Silvergate and Signature;
9. The US House of Representatives passed a budget plan to lay the foundation for Trump's tax cuts and raising the debt ceiling.
